Package: gnome-shell-ubuntu-communitheme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: GNOME Shell Ubuntu Community Theme
 This is the theme that is shaped by the community on the Ubuntu hub.
 .
 This package contains the GNOME Shell theme part
 .
 More information if you want to follow the development on
 https://community.ubuntu.com/c/desktop/theme-refresh.

Package: ubuntu-communitheme-session
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         gnome-shell-ubuntu-communitheme (= ${source:Version}),
Description: session starting Ubuntu Community Theme
 This is the session enabling starting easily the theme
 that is shaped by the community on the Ubuntu hub.
 .
 This package contains the session part, adding an "Ubuntu CommuniTheme"
 session to GDM. It has the same caracterists than the ubuntu session,
 apart from the default themes (GNOME Shell, GTK, GDMâ€¦)
 .
 More information if you want to follow the development on
 https://community.ubuntu.com/c/desktop/theme-refresh.
